data.description: New price $420,000. If being outside of the hustle and bustle is what you're searching for, then this home is for you. Nestled within the beautiful landscapes of Juliana's Garden, this home not only offers space and functionality, but an entire community that takes pride and integrity in maintaining the charm and appeal of the neighborhood. Find yourself enjoying sunset walks through the rose garden, around the neighborhood, or enjoying the views around you. The home offers 3 bedrooms, two bathrooms, OWNED SOLAR, and a large backyard ready for entertaining. Make this home yours just in time for the Holiday season.
